<bibRefCitation author="Jesus &amp; Fonseca" box="[611,864,189,215]" firstAuthor="Jesus" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="343 - 349" refId="ref184868" refString="Jesus, D. C. &amp; Fonseca, L. C. (1999) First records of 13 echinoderm species on the southwest coast of Portugal. Boletin Instituto Espanol de Oceanografia, 15 (1 - 4), 343 - 349." type="journal article" year="1999">Jesus &amp; Fonseca 1999</bibRefCitation>
